{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":169422,"duration_api_ms":158864,"num_turns":11,"result":"## Summary\n\n| Issue | Root Cause | Effect | Fix |\n|-------|-----------|--------|-----|\n| NPE in LabelService | `__labels__` is null when no rules match | StageExecutor catches → SYSTEM_ERROR → 3 retries → all fail → stuck | `getOrDefault(\"__labels__\", Map.of())` |\n| Stage advances on failure | Line 209 unconditionally sets `nextStage` | Failed entities written as LABELED instead of PENDING; recovery can't re-run the correct stage | Only call `setProcessingStage(nextStage)` when `serviceSuccess == true` |\n\nAfter fix #2, entities that fail labeling will stay in `PENDING` with an error code, making it clear they need labeling retried (not policy evaluation). Existing stuck entities in LABELED with non-zero codes should be reset to `PENDING` with `processingCode=0` to re-enter the pipeline.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"a8b78aff-8318-44d2-b7e0-198f57a677bc","total_cost_usd":0.67293985,"usage":{"input_tokens":511,"cache_creation_input_tokens":31270,"cache_read_input_tokens":213613,"output_tokens":4426,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":31270,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":511,"outputTokens":4426,"cacheReadInputTokens":213613,"cacheCreationInputTokens":31270,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.41544899999999996,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":203,"outputTokens":5519,"cacheReadInputTokens":1172391,"cacheCreationInputTokens":89963,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.25749085000000005,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"55d210c0-cd06-4b97-a510-eac1d57cbd71"}
